{"tid":1334312,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[召喚歷史JJ] 一齊黎討論英國當年將香港\"回歸\" 中國的決定","createTime":"2019-07-20T05:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T11:41:41.000Z","uid":265659,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"eaeff7f0cb566476b82bf7179384bc9950578773","tid":1334312,"uid":265659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T05:09:24.000Z","msg":"好似倪匡先生咁講，香港當年的情況，九七唔應該用&quot;回歸&quot;呢個字眼黎形容，對於呢點我同意，個人咁睇，因為香港被割讓的時候，當年中國的合法政權係國民黨，到九七期限之際，點解要&quot;回歸&quot;共產黨？唔make sense.<br />\n<br />\n而且唔同當年滿清政權繼承比國民黨，滿清完敗令國民黨成為當時中國土地的合法政權；九七之際，國民黨只係打輸咗，但未被消失，而係走佬去台灣，咁點解香港唔係&quot;回歸&quot;割讓時候的政權國民黨？而係&quot;回歸&quot;因打敗國民黨而佔領中國土地的&quot;共產黨&quot;? 唔係應該跟政權而去跟土地？我借咗屋企啲野俾你，你唔係還借俾你的我，而係還俾趕我出屋企的生蕃？<br />\n<br />\n覺得香港的命運，被一個香港土地權暫時擁有者（英國）隨意決定，覺得好嬲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無歷史JJ 一齊討論，正反論點都歡迎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05bcb32a7383cbf977746771bf3332a882d4148","tid":1334312,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T05:10:38.000Z","msg":"係咩原因令英國放棄香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d800fddca1cfd09b8cf49af6a9d70ab35d3d6a","tid":1334312,"uid":265659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a05bcb32a7383cbf977746771bf3332a882d4148","tid":1334312,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T05:10:38.000Z","msg":"係咩原因令英國放棄香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T05:13:20.000Z","msg":"想奶共？<br />\n畢竟當時共產黨掌握咗中國的領土，吸引力比走佬去台灣大？<br />\n而且聽聞當時美國都支持台灣，英國好似蘇聯咁想扶直一個可以抗衡的力量？<br />\n<br />\n利申非歷史JJ"},{"pid":"5a89e1aa38d3fefba169f9944ef79b632230c43f","tid":1334312,"uid":265659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a05bcb32a7383cbf977746771bf3332a882d4148","tid":1334312,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T05:10:38.000Z","msg":"係咩原因令英國放棄香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T05:16:47.000Z","msg":"而且會唔會同英國帝國主義沒落，去到後殖民時期，放生好多殖民地獨立，利益&lt;管冶成本，送俾共產黨廢事破壞同中國關係？"},{"pid":"63f319268feb09e68a235fbb9059d1525970e1e0","tid":1334312,"uid":265659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T05:37:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87f939be7ae8c5f272328cc0910f8b4b98935517","tid":1334312,"uid":282925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:02:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為香港被割讓的時候，當年中國的合法政權係國民黨</blockquote><br />\n當時嘅合法政權唔係清政府？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3097d5270aefbb5dd1bc7fc09a9dac9c41fb395e","tid":1334312,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a05bcb32a7383cbf977746771bf3332a882d4148","tid":1334312,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T05:10:38.000Z","msg":"係咩原因令英國放棄香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:06:44.000Z","msg":"我拋下磚先<br />\n<br />\n1. 國力問題: 啱啱打完福克蘭未回到氣 加上嗰排經濟唔好<br />\n2. 民意問題: 香港人唔特別抗拒中共<br />\n3. 法律問題: 英國一早承認咗中共先係代表中國 而99年大限冇得作假"},{"pid":"35664fa5e79cc79c9ef8aa0dcac93eca87835ae9","tid":1334312,"uid":265659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87f939be7ae8c5f272328cc0910f8b4b98935517","tid":1334312,"uid":282925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:02:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為香港被割讓的時候，當年中國的合法政權係國民黨</blockquote><br />\n當時嘅合法政權唔係清政府？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:32:13.000Z","msg":"係，但滿清向國民政府投降，好合理咁繼承咗清政府的所有野。<br />\n<br />\n而且清政府都已經唔存在，但國民黨政府仲存在呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人愚見"},{"pid":"c97e3a3ee8d1cf5b792476d36db0b5414882ea1c","tid":1334312,"uid":282925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:38:31.000Z","msg":"我既睇法係如果你係講合理性嘅話，咁英國將香港歸還比台灣（亦即係中華民國）當然係合情合理啦。奈何中華人民共和國勢力大，所謂誰大誰惡誰正確，英國將香港歸還比中華人民共和國都算係無可奈何"},{"pid":"317e7e75789a59fd47f904c73d19adfb6760f367","tid":1334312,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:38:52.000Z","msg":"要跟美國聯中滅蘇"},{"pid":"d0fc0cd240c83ac3393d2933f4e31285ce05be66","tid":1334312,"uid":265659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c97e3a3ee8d1cf5b792476d36db0b5414882ea1c","tid":1334312,"uid":282925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:38:31.000Z","msg":"我既睇法係如果你係講合理性嘅話，咁英國將香港歸還比台灣（亦即係中華民國）當然係合情合理啦。奈何中華人民共和國勢力大，所謂誰大誰惡誰正確，英國將香港歸還比中華人民共和國都算係無可奈何"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:37:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家諗番被事頭婆出賣 好唔甘心"},{"pid":"ad0aeae2afd24c75a635a5820584c601327bcede","tid":1334312,"uid":185712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35664fa5e79cc79c9ef8aa0dcac93eca87835ae9","tid":1334312,"uid":265659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87f939be7ae8c5f272328cc0910f8b4b98935517","tid":1334312,"uid":282925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:02:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為香港被割讓的時候，當年中國的合法政權係國民黨</blockquote><br />\n當時嘅合法政權唔係清政府？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:32:13.000Z","msg":"係，但滿清向國民政府投降，好合理咁繼承咗清政府的所有野。<br />\n<br />\n而且清政府都已經唔存在，但國民黨政府仲存在呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.