ke":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:32:13.000Z","msg":"係，但滿清向國民政府投降，好合理咁繼承咗清政府的所有野。<br />\n<br />\n而且清政府都已經唔存在，但國民黨政府仲存在呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人愚見"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:21:29.000Z","msg":"係中華民國<br />\n<br />\n孫文既中國國民黨在1919年先改組而成，國民黨之後北伐奪取了中華民國的正統<br />\n<br />\n1949年中共就國號問題，本來係有意沿用中華民國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:29:24.000Z","msg":"咁姐係中華民國的國民黨政府理論上先係合法拎番香港的政府？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T10:42:18.000Z","msg":"可以咁講  <br />\n你買野要拎野都要張單既正本 <br />\n唔通你比副本就拎到咩 人地睬你都傻<br />\n正本割讓條約一直都中華民國手中<br />\n不過當時拳頭問題 要比番中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe90d81f041f2ad39d807cb579627cb028d6d3c","tid":1334312,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T11:33:13.000Z","msg":"其實好簡單 <br />\n鬼叫香港呢撻地係痴實中國大陸<br />\n而唔係隔個海？"},{"pid":"2dce866ba2301f2bcd5d41e8c8557f54a712b2db","tid":1334312,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T11:41:41.000Z","msg":"蘋果2014年報導：<br />\n<br />\nLink<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140205/18615623\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140205%2F18615623&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbjbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=41ed396f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140205%2F18615623&h=ab38eb7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140205/18615623</a><br />\n<br />\n英方又指絕大部份港人都是華人，對英國無感情聯繫，故不擬討論港人自決前途權利，更明言「不會堅持談判結果一定要與港人意願一致（nor insist that any solution must be in line with their wishes）」，談判目標是與中國達成協議，令香港繼續繁榮，讓英國有機會賺錢（Our aim is an agreement with China under which the territory continues to prosper in a way that provides opportunities for Britain to make money）。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20141231/18986739\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20141231%2F18986739&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbjbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=d04fb63b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20141231%2F18986739&h=d117e1b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20141231/18986739</a><br />\n<br />\n新一批解密文件中，有一封外相賀維私人秘書里基茨的信件，透露賀維與戴卓爾夫人曾考慮帶同包括GEC的商界成員訪京，但諮詢港督尤德後擔心會被香港傳媒大肆報道，造成「我們將香港賣給中國後，現在收到獎品（getting our prize for having sold out Hong Kong to the Chinese）」的印象而打消念頭。"}]}